OL,11,Frevealed that 684 children were
OL,12,Freferred to the Child and Adolescent
OL,13,FMental Health Service (CAHMS) in 2023
OL,14,Fcompared to 585 the previous year.
OL,16,FThe report also found that adult out-
OL,17,Fpatient referrals to specialist mental
OL,18,Fhealth services had increased by 10%
OL,19,Fsince 2022 - there were 1677 in 2023
OL,20,Fcompared to 1327 in 2022.
